Class Trie<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tudarmstadt.ukp.dkpro.core.io.pdf.Trie<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - the value type.

    public class Trie<V>
extends Object
    A HashMap-based Trie. Zero-length or null keys are not allowed. Null values are allowed.
